claim: There is a period of time that starts from the end of the Cretaceous Period million years ago.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The Cretaceous  (  -LSB- pronkrᵻˈteɪʃəs -RSB- ,  )  is a geologic period and system that spans 79 million years from the end of the Jurassic Period million years ago  (  Mya  )  to the beginning of the Paleogene Period Mya .
